com.geouniq.android

Interface GeoUniq.IMotionActivityListener

  • Enclosing class:
    GeoUniq

    public static interface GeoUniq.IMotionActivityListener
    Defines methods to receive a callback when a motion activity starts or ends.
    Implementing this interface is necessary to call the methods GeoUniq.registerMotionActivityListener(MotionActivity[], Class, IErrorListener) and GeoUniq.removeMotionActivityListener(MotionActivity[], Class).
